data.description: This charming, well-maintained single-story, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is ready for new adventures!  Check out the bonus rooms located throughout the house; bring your tape measure to verify the dimensions of the garage-converted den. The kitchen stove, central heater, and washer/dryer connections are all electric. Get cozy during the winter days in the family room with the wood-burning fireplace. Don't miss the front yard's centerpiece: a majestic, grand old tree that has stood tall for generations. Its expansive branches reach toward the sky, providing a natural canopy of shade for centuries. Schedule your showing today before it's too late!
